template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:12:- `target_scope` (scope ou entité qui reprend)
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:20:1. Lire la feature + son worklog.
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:21:2. Vérifier que `progress.phase` est cohérent (pas `done` — utiliser `feature-done` à la place).
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:22:3. Si le scope courant n'a pas d'evidence (build/tests passants) → warn mais autoriser sur confirmation user.
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:44:- `progress.phase` → `spec` si target va re-spec, `implement` sinon (demander)
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:45:- `progress.step` → `"handoff pending → <target_scope>"`
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:46:- `progress.resume_hint` → `"voir HANDOFF du <date> dans worklog"`
template/.ai/workflows/feature-handoff.md.jinja:47:- `progress.updated` → date du jour
